data.name: Google Darkest Fusion 2/2
data.description: Do you like my style? Please support my work and fund me a coffee (via PayPal to the left of "Install" button). Also share style with your friends. Thank you for being awesome! Darkest Fusion supports almost every Google site. Due to an style size limit Darkest Fusion has been divided into 2 parts. That part contains dark theme for less used Google sites: Developers, Firebase, Docs, Forms, Flights, Play, Music, Scholar and Script. First style is available >>> there <<< Keep and Support currently have stock dark themes. Originally based on great work by DeathTBO who abandoned his project so I decided to continue his work by rebuilting everything from scratch. I hope you like my vision for Dark Google :)

data.name: Google - Dark & light - Custom background & colors
data.description:
IMPORTANT!!! - To choose your own colors, backgrounds, theme color and options, click on the "Customize Settings" button below

Features:
Change Google style to a based on Material Design improving the visibility of search results. This theme allows to choose between Dark Theme and Light Theme, and have options to hide or show several page elements. Also allows to choose your own colors for links, background images for Google homepage, and search page.

By default:

  • Light theme is selected.
  • Orange is the color for visited links.
  • The backgrounds are those that can be seen on the xample images.

data.name: FelisFire: Highlight Patch and Crafting Items
data.description: The FelisFire version of the "Flight Rising: Highlight Swipp & Baldwin Items v2" by Zoga. Patch items, items used in Casey's Crafting, and items used in events are highlighted or outlined. Items used in Casey's Crafting are back-lit in purple Patch items are outlined in red. Event items are outlined in blue. Highlighted Event Items are: Candle Wax, Doubloon, Rabbit, and Rabbit Foot. (Discs, Orbs, Grams, and Easter Eggs are not highlighted.) NOTE: This does not provide an advantage when gathering. The highlighting/outlining does not show above the panel before you click a square. You cannot see what's under the panels.

data.name: Gmail transparent background
data.description:
Turns the inbox fields transparent if they are empty, so that the Gmail background will show if you have a Gmail theme applied.
Emails still have a white background applied to keep them legible and prevent interfering with HTML emails with their own styles.

data.name: Imprimable - Fruits et légumes de saisons
data.description:
Cette feuille de style permet d'avoir la liste sur un papier quand on va au marché.

Elle effectue les transformations suivantes :

- retire les éléments superflus
- affiche chaque mois sur une page séparée
- retire les mois que vous avez masqués par un clic
- affiche le tout sur fond blanc pour économiser l'encre
